1
00:00:30,260 --> 00:00:31,060
Your Majesty.

2
00:00:31,430 --> 00:00:32,400
In my opinion,

3
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:34,930
those great imperial families are the cancer of the human race.

4
00:00:34,930 --> 00:00:36,530
Since they are the pillars of the human race,

5
00:00:36,530 --> 00:00:39,160
they should contribute their imperial scriptures and weapons,

6
00:00:39,160 --> 00:00:41,730
so all cultivators in the world can bathe in the imperial grace.

7
00:00:41,730 --> 00:00:43,630
They shouldn't be so selfish.

8
00:00:45,430 --> 00:00:47,660
These families disrespect the Ancestral Court,

9
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:50,260
relying entirely on their ancestors' legacy.

10
00:00:50,330 --> 00:00:52,600
Why not make them hand over their imperial weapons and scriptures

11
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:54,530
for the Ancestral Court to manage?

12
00:00:54,660 --> 00:00:56,260
Without these,

13
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:58,430
they will have to obey.

14
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,330
You are absolutely right.

15
00:01:01,700 --> 00:01:03,300
At the Human Emperor Ceremony,

16
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:04,430
I will propose this.

17
00:01:04,629 --> 00:01:05,500
Furthermore,

18
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:08,660
to consolidate the Ancestral Court's authority,

19
00:01:08,660 --> 00:01:09,660
I suggest

20
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:13,700
Your Majesty order the families to send their strongest cultivators to guard the Imperial Pass.

21
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:15,600
Without the Ancestral Court's edict,

22
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:16,960
they cannot leave.

23
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:19,630
That makes sense.

24
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:25,130
But there has been no movement at the Imperial Pass for thousands of years.

25
00:01:25,130 --> 00:01:26,760
What reason should we use

26
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:28,200
to send them there?

27
00:01:29,230 --> 00:01:30,760
It's actually very simple.

28
00:01:31,030 --> 00:01:33,430
Your Majesty only needs someone to light

29
00:01:34,229 --> 00:01:37,100
the Blood Wolf Smoke at the Imperial Pass.

30
00:01:43,630 --> 00:01:44,759
Yun'er, this is bad!

31
00:01:44,930 --> 00:01:47,000
Something happened at the Imperial Pass!

32
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,600
That crazy woman Luo Jinghong,

33
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,530
I don't know why,

34
00:01:49,729 --> 00:01:50,789
suddenly went mad.

35
00:01:52,430 --> 00:01:53,360
Get lost!

36
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:55,590
I want to see the Inspector.

37
00:02:00,330 --> 00:02:01,030
What?

38
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,800
Instead of fighting the demons at the Imperial Pass,

39
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,400
she dared to neglect her duty

40
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,000
and even kill the Inspector?

41
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:08,800
Maybe the matter of the Luo clan

42
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,860
was discovered by her.

43
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:10,860
How could that be?

44
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:12,330
The Luo clan has long been demoted to a sin clan,

45
00:02:12,330 --> 00:02:13,200
most were slaughtered,

46
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,200
and the rest exiled to the Sin Village.

47
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,460
Who tipped her off?

48
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,160
Pass down my edict.

49
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:20,530
Luo Jinghong colluded with the demons,

50
00:02:20,530 --> 00:02:21,930
betrayed the human race,

51
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:24,160
and slaughtered the garrison at the Imperial Pass.

52
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,960
Now, in the Tianxuan Continent,

53
00:02:26,329 --> 00:02:28,260
everyone has the right to kill her.

54
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:29,800
Report!

55
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:30,930
Report!

56
00:02:31,260 --> 00:02:32,060
Your Majesty,

57
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,630
the patriarchs of the four great families (Jin, Xiao, Jiang, Wang)

58
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:35,000
are kneeling outside, begging for an audience,

59
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,230
crying out loudly.

60
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,260
Let them in.

61
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:39,660
Yun'er,

62
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:43,660
our four families risked our lives to elect you as the Mandate Human Emperor.

63
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,630
Today, you must seek justice for us!

64
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:48,900
Relying on his high cultivation level,

65
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,730
Gu Linyuan ignored the fellowship of the human race,

66
00:02:50,730 --> 00:02:53,230
slaughtered our ancestors in the Sin Village,

67
00:02:53,230 --> 00:02:55,530
and even took the Xiao clan's imperial weapon.

68
00:02:55,530 --> 00:02:57,860
Please seek justice for us, Your Majesty.

69
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,400
Your Majesty.

70
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:02,960
Gu Linyuan is harboring the remnants of the Luo Clan's sinful bloodline.

71
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:05,430
He must have colluded with the Demon Clan long ago.

72
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:08,500
I implore Your Majesty to issue an Emperor's decree immediately,

73
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:11,330
calling upon all righteous forces in the Tianxuan Continent

74
00:03:11,330 --> 00:03:13,030
to crusade against the Gu Family together.

75
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:13,690
How dare he.

76
00:03:13,930 --> 00:03:15,800
I've long heard that Gu Linyuan is brutal

77
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,860
and bloodthirsty,

78
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:20,130
but I never expected that against the pillars of our human race,

79
00:03:20,130 --> 00:03:21,900
he would dare to strike so ruthlessly.

80
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,260
Our great imperial families

81
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:25,530
have made great contributions to protecting the human race.

82
00:03:25,530 --> 00:03:27,060
The fall of every patriarch

83
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:29,500
is an irreparable loss to our human race.

84
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:32,130
Gu Linyuan's actions are destroying the foundation of our human race.

85
00:03:32,130 --> 00:03:33,990
Men, draft a decree immediately.

86
00:03:34,230 --> 00:03:35,829
Pass on my Emperor's decree.

87
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:40,000
Order Gu Linyuan to come to the Human Ancestral Court to beg for forgiveness within three days,

88
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,500
and return the Xiao Clan's Imperial Weapon.

89
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:44,460
Otherwise, don't blame me for disregarding our past ties.

90
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:47,430
I will personally gather all human forces in the world

91
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,130
to flatten his Gu Family in the Eastern Wasteland.

92
00:03:49,130 --> 00:03:50,660
Your Majesty is wise.

93
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,100
Long live the Emperor!

94
00:03:52,100 --> 00:03:53,260
Your Majesty is wise.

95
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:54,530
Long live the Emperor!

96
00:04:06,260 --> 00:04:09,720
Go find a blessed land rich in spiritual energy to settle them.

97
00:04:09,830 --> 00:04:12,400
Thank you, Emperor Gu, for saving our lives.

98
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:20,660
Third.

99
00:04:21,329 --> 00:04:24,100
I, Ji Qingchen, pay my respects to you, Master's wife.

100
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:27,100
Rumor has it that the daughter of the Phoenix Emperor is domineering.

101
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,130
I hope she doesn't misunderstand

102
00:04:28,130 --> 00:04:30,230
the pure relationship between my master and me.

103
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:31,730
Instead of cultivating in seclusion in Qihuang Palace,

104
00:04:31,730 --> 00:04:33,130
how do you have the mood to come find me?

105
00:04:33,130 --> 00:04:35,830
Don't you know what kind of disaster you've provoked?

106
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:38,830
They are just a bunch of clowns at the Human Ancestral Court.

107
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,300
Don't mind them.

108
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:41,000
I've warned you.

109
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:44,200
Anyway, unless it's your human race's internal mess,

110
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:47,430
I won't let the Primordial Clans help you.

111
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:49,300
Don't worry, my wife.

112
00:04:49,659 --> 00:04:51,060
In front of me,

113
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:53,260
they can't make any waves.

114
00:04:55,130 --> 00:04:56,730
I didn't expect this arrogant woman

115
00:04:56,730 --> 00:04:58,659
to actually come and care about me.

116
00:04:59,130 --> 00:05:01,130
One night of marriage brings a hundred days of grace.

117
00:05:01,130 --> 00:05:04,860
The ancients did not deceive me.
